divs: Sighting Detailsi was in new york on a trip with a group of people i know. we had bought tickets for a double decker bus tour around the city on june 5th. it was evening time around 5:00-7:00. we were on the bus tour and we were taking pictures. i had taken pictures of the new york times building. i never went through the pictures until today june 30th, 2013. i was looking through the pictures and saw a dark blimp like structure in the sky next to the new york times building. i never auctually saw it in real life but it showed up in my pictures.
